<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RGVL - Dados Pessoais</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --bg: #0f0f0f; --bg-card: #1a1a1a; --text: #fff; --text-secondary: #a0a0a0; --text-muted: #666; --accent: #6366f1; --accent-green: #10b981; --accent-blue: #3b82f6; --accent-orange: #f59e0b; --accent-pink: #ec4899; --border: #2a2a2a; --shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); --radius: 12px; }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); min-height: 100vh; padding-bottom: 2rem; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e); padding: 2rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .header-content { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
        .logo { width: 48px; height: 48px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-blue)); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        .header-text h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; }
        .header-text .subtitle { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.85rem; }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1.5rem 1rem; }
        .section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .section-title { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
        .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .stat-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; }
        .stat-value { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); }
        .stat-label { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
        .profile-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
        .profile-avatar { width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-pink)); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; }
        .profile-info h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .profile-info .role { color: var(--text-secondary); }
        .profile-info .details { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
        .profile-info .detail-item { font-size: 0.85rem; }
        .profile-info .detail-label { color: var(--text-muted); display: block; }
        .family-grid, .companies-grid, .properties-grid, .legal-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
        .family-card, .company-card, .property-card, .legal-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; }
        .family-avatar { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-pink), var(--accent-orange)); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        .family-name { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .family-relationship { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .family-details { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .family-details span { display: block; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
        .company-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .company-name { font-weight: 600; }
        .company-status { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(16,185,129,0.2); color: var(--accent-green); }
        .company-status.inactive { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.2); color: #ef4444; }
        .company-cnpj { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: monospace; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .company-info { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
        .company-info span { display: block; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
        .company-capital { margin-top: 0.75rem; padding-top: 0.75rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .company-capital strong { color: var(--accent-green); }
        .property-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .property-type { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.2); color: var(--accent); }
        .property-status { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(16,185,129,0.2); color: var(--accent-green); }
        .property-address { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .property-neighborhood { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .property-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 0.5rem; padding-top: 0.75rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .property-stat { text-align: center; }
        .property-stat-value { font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); }
        .property-stat-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .property-value { margin-top: 0.75rem; padding-top: 0.75rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .property-value strong { color: var(--accent-green); }
        .legal-card { border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-orange); }
        .legal-number { font-family: monospace; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .legal-court { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0.25rem 0; }
        .legal-subject { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .legal-parties { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .legal-status { display: inline-block; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 4px; background: rgba(16,185,129,0.2); color: var(--accent-green); font-size: 0.75rem; }
        .legal-filings { margin-top: 0.75rem; padding-top: 0.75rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .legal-filing { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .list-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; }
        .list-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; padding: 0.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .list-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .list-avatar { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--bg); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 600; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .list-info { flex: 1; }
        .list-name { font-weight: 500; }
        .list-meta { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
        @media(max-width:640px) { .header-content { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; } .profile-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .profile-avatar { margin: 0 auto; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
                <div class="logo">R</div>
                <div class="header-text"><h1>RGVL - Dados Pessoais</h1><div class="subtitle">Rodrigo Gorgulho de Vasconcellos Lanna</div></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="stats-grid" id="statsGrid">
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-value" id="statCompanies">-</div><div class="stat-label">Empresas</div></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-value" id="statProperties">-</div><div class="stat-label">Imóveis</div></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-value" id="statNetWorth">-</div><div class="stat-label">Patrimônio</div></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-value" id="statProcesses">-</div><div class="stat-label">Processos</div></div>
        </div>
        <section class="section"><h2 class="section-title">👤 Identificação</h2><div class="profile-card" id="profileCard"></div></section>
        <section class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">👨‍👩‍👧 Família</h2>
            <div class="stats-grid" style="margin-bottom:1rem"><div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-value" id="familySpouseCount">-</div><div class="stat-label">Cônjuge</div></div>
            <div class="stats-grid" style="margin-bottom:1rem"><div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-value" id="familySiblingsCount">-</div><div class="stat-label">Irmãos</div></div>
            <div class="stats-grid" style="margin-bottom:1rem"><div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-value" id="familyNephewsCount">-</div><div class="stat-label">Sobrinhos</div></div>
            <div class="family-grid" id="familyGrid"></div>
        </section>
        <section class="section"><h2 class="section-title">🏢 Empresas</h2><div class="companies-grid" id="companiesGrid"></div></section>
        <section class="section"><h2 class="section-title">🏠 Imóveis</h2><div class="properties-grid" id="propertiesGrid"></div></section>
        <section class="section"><h2 class="section-title">📞 Contatos</h2><div class="list-card" id="contactsCard"></div></section>
        <section class="section"><h2 class="section-title">📄 Documentos</h2><div class="list-card" id="documentsCard"></div></section>
        <section class="section"><h2 class="section-title">⚖️ Processos Jurídicos</h2><div class="legal-grid" id="legalGrid"></div></section>
    </div>
